<org.eclipse.epf.uma:PracticeDescription xmi:version="2.0" xmlns:xmi="http://www.omg.org/XMI" xmlns:org.eclipse.epf.uma="http://www.eclipse.org/epf/uma/1.0.6/uma.ecore" xmlns:epf="http://www.eclipse.org/epf" epf:version="1.5.1" xmlns:rmc="http://www.ibm.com/rmc" rmc:version="7.5.1" xmi:id="-8QZ26x7VmUMjGs9suMCwAA" name="eg_bl_bpl_crm,_ciM90JsJEeOMG9JzPmKf0Q" guid="-8QZ26x7VmUMjGs9suMCwAA" changeDate="2015-02-07T13:29:42.880-0500" version="7.5.1">
  <problem>&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;>&#xD;
    &lt;img alt=&quot;Manage Customer Profile Process&quot; src=&quot;./resources/BL-Business-Res-Manage-Customer-Profile.png&quot; />&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    A customer account manager works with the customer to updates subscriptions as specified in their profile.&#xD;
&lt;/p></problem>
  <goals>&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Receive Customer Input&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Customers provide information on the Information Needs of interest to them. The following steps apply:&amp;nbsp;&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ol>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Input from the Customer is received;&amp;nbsp;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        The current Customer profile is consulted and the required changes verified with the Customer;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        The required changes are summarized.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ol>&#xD;
&lt;h5>&#xD;
    Inputs&#xD;
&lt;/h5>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Information Needs and other information from Customers.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h5>&#xD;
    Outputs&#xD;
&lt;/h5>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Summary of required changes&amp;nbsp;to the Customer Profile.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h5>&#xD;
    Exceptions&#xD;
&lt;/h5>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    None.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h5>&#xD;
    State Changes&#xD;
&lt;/h5>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    None.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    &lt;br />&#xD;
    Update Customer Profile&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Customer profiles are updated as required. If no profile exists, one is created.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ol>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        The change summary is compared to the current customer profile;&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Required changes are made and saved..&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ol>&#xD;
&lt;h5>&#xD;
    Inputs&#xD;
&lt;/h5>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Summary of required changes&amp;nbsp;to the Customer Profile.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h5>&#xD;
    Outputs&#xD;
&lt;/h5>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Update profile.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h5>&#xD;
    Exceptions&#xD;
&lt;/h5>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    None.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h5>&#xD;
    State Changes&#xD;
&lt;/h5>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    None.&#xD;
&lt;/p></goals>
